{"tid":859672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「一人一post」呼籲星期日一齊去遊行","createTime":"2018-10-12T16:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T05:13:17.000Z","uid":87030,"like":109,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"fc93916eeab1e34811a9944b77e8ce87455c3fae","tid":859672,"uid":87030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔知到時會有幾多人<br />\n即使唔合理我都會同自己講：<br />\n<br />\n我去，大家都會去<br />\n<br />\n就算留言幾多負面言論我都唔會理<br />\n因為喱次阻唔到，香港就乜柒都無。<br />\n<br />\n你未來至少14年既社會福利都會受影響<br />\n所以唔好再覺得同你無關<br />\n<br />\n你唔爭取，第時比大陸狗笑騎騎袋你辛苦賺既錢交既稅，你甘心咩？<br />\n<br />\n你甘心未來交比政府既錢，都繼續斷送比無貢獻無付出既大陸狗咩？<br />\n<br />\n你甘心咩？<br />\n<br />\n10月14日 銅鑼灣東角道 3點為香港剩低既少少希望掙扎<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫手一人一post"},{"pid":"213ce27d604d4e67d21257545f137ad8b87b72a1","tid":859672,"uid":144685,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:53:07.000Z","msg":"去硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7cff509e1d3a80c3e3758444928789119ff40f","tid":859672,"uid":66527,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:04:21.000Z","msg":"佔中2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8def8f5e8e242139a0c4df3cbb5efa424e6deb97","tid":859672,"uid":89520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:18:29.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"bc3e4c2fc0d2b67ecfaf61921356ef20e30b7620","tid":859672,"uid":5419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T18:49:01.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bfc077a27c3cc18a935c1cb9cdc1483e05ba2d","tid":859672,"uid":204565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T18:50:03.000Z","msg":"推撚到見報啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8035b13e2b73b8d79886c63f5f156220537bca9c","tid":859672,"uid":204565,"like":0,"dislik